1113
01:10:39.257 --> 01:10:40.456
[GASPS]

1114
01:10:40.458 --> 01:10:42.194
[PANTING]

1115
01:10:49.100 --> 01:10:51.735
[♪♪♪]

1116
01:11:09.020 --> 01:11:10.055
Brandon?

1117
01:11:11.656 --> 01:11:12.857
Oh. man.

1118
01:11:20.199 --> 01:11:21.200
