1156
01:14:11.341 --> 01:14:13.042
[WHISPERS]
Please help me.

1157
01:14:15.011 --> 01:14:16.112
Please...

1158
01:14:17.414 --> 01:14:18.613
OPERATOR [ON PHONE]:
